  PIC6_BIRD: "Bird, Tokyo 2018 spring",
  APPTITLE4: "A Poem, a process, alchemy",
  APP9: "Two tiny eggs in the alchemical bird's nest",
  APP10: "Dream the undreamable",
  APP11: "Speak the unspeakable",
  APP12: "Feel the “unfeelable”",
  APP13: "Formulate the unformulated",
  APP14: "Experience the incomprehensible",
  APP15: "The glimmering golden egg encapsulates our whole world",
  APP16: "We entangle, we disentangle — and begin again",
  APP17: "When things start making sense and becoming meaningful, psychic transformation can occur in the process. Like alchemy, raw materials are gradually transformed into gold. What may emerge is a greater self-awareness, a fuller sense of self, a deeper capacity to embrace the not-knowing in life, and a greater ability to make decisions without repeating unhealthy patterns.",
  APPTITLE5: "Jungian Sandplay",
